#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "FreeBSD as a Host with bhyve"
msgstr ""
"在FreeBSD上使用bhyve作为主机\n"
"\n"
"bhyve是FreeBSD操作系统中的一个虚拟化系统，它允许您在FreeBSD上运行虚拟机。它使用虚拟机管理器（VMM）和硬件虚拟化来提供高效的虚拟化解决方案。\n"
"\n"
"作为一个主机系统，FreeBSD提供了广泛的支持和功能，使其成为一个强大的选择。您可以在FreeBSD上安装bhyve，并使用它来创建和管理虚拟机。\n"
"\n"
"使用bhyve作为主机，您可以轻松地运行多个虚拟机，每个虚拟机都可以运行自己的操作系统和应用程序。您可以为每个虚拟机分配不同的资源，并根据需要对其进行调整。\n"
"\n"
"另外，bhyve提供了与其他虚拟化系统相似的功能，如快照、网络连接和存储管理。您可以使用这些功能来管理和配置虚拟机，以满足您的特定需求。\n"
"\n"
"总而言之，FreeBSD作为一个主机系统和bhyve作为虚拟化解决方案的组合，为您提供了一个高性能和灵活的方式来部署和管理虚拟机环境。无论您是在开发、测试还是生产环境中，都可以从这个强大的组合中受益。"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:499
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The bhyve BSD-licensed hypervisor became part of the base system with "
"FreeBSD 10.0-RELEASE.  This hypervisor supports a number of guests, "
"including FreeBSD, OpenBSD, and many Linux(R) distributions.  By default, "
"bhyve provides access to serial console and does not emulate a graphical "
"console.  Virtualization offload features of newer CPUs are used to avoid "
"the legacy methods of translating instructions and manually managing memory "
"mappings."
msgstr ""
"在FreeBSD "
"10.0-RELEASE中，BSD许可的bhyve虚拟机监控器成为了基本系统的一部分。该虚拟机监控器支持许多客户机操作系统，包括FreeBSD、OpenBSD和许多Linux(R)发行版。默认情况下，bhyve提供串行控制台访问，不支持图形控制台仿真。较新的CPU的虚拟化卸载功能被用来避免传统的指令转换和手动管理内存映射的方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/virtualization/_index.adoc:507
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The bhyve design requires a processor that supports Intel(R) Extended Page "
"Tables (EPT) or AMD(R) Rapid Virtualization Indexing (RVI) or Nested Page "
"Tables (NPT).  Hosting Linux(R) guests or FreeBSD guests with more than one "
"vCPU requires VMX unrestricted mode support (UG).  Most newer processors, "
"specifically the Intel(R) Core(TM) i3/i5/i7 and Intel(R) Xeon(TM) E3/E5/E7, "
"support these features.  UG support was introduced with Intel's Westmere "
"micro-architecture.  For a complete list of Intel(R) processors that support"
" EPT, refer to "
"https://ark.intel.com/content/www/us/en/ark/search/featurefilter.html?productType=873&0_ExtendedPageTables=True[]."
"  RVI is found on the third generation and later of the AMD Opteron(TM) "
"(Barcelona) processors.  The easiest way to tell if a processor supports "
"bhyve is to run `dmesg` or look in [.filename]#/var/run/dmesg.boot# for the "
"`POPCNT` processor feature flag on the `Features2` line for AMD(R) "
"processors or `EPT` and `UG` on the `VT-x` line for Intel(R) processors."
msgstr ""
"bhyve的设计要求处理器支持Intel(R)的扩展页表(EPT)，或者AMD(R)的快速虚拟化索引(RVI)，或者嵌套页表(NPT)。在托管Linux(R)客户机或者FreeBSD客户机且需要多于一个虚拟CPU时，需要支持VMX的非限制模式(UG)。大多数较新的处理器，特别是Intel(R)"
" Core(TM) i3/i5/i7和Intel(R) Xeon(TM) "
"E3/E5/E7，都支持这些特性。UG支持从Intel的Westmere微架构开始引入。要查看支持EPT的Intel(R)处理器的完整列表，请参阅https://ark.intel.com/content/www/us/en/ark/search/featurefilter.html?productType=873&0_ExtendedPageTables=True[]。RVI出现在第三代及以后的AMD"
" Opteron(TM) "
"(Barcelona)处理器上。判断处理器是否支持bhyve的最简单方法是运行'dmesg'命令或查看位于[.filename]#/var/run/dmesg.boot#的文件中AMD(R)处理器的`Features2`行上的`POPCNT`处理器特性标志，或者Intel(R)处理器的`VT-x`行上的`EPT`和`UG`特性标志。"

